@startuml
title 计价管道计算流程 (Price Calculation Pipeline)

actor User as "买家"
participant OrderCore as "order-core"
participant PriceSvc as "price-service"
participant MemberSvc as "member-service\n(ADR-046)"
participant PromoSvc as "promotion-service"
participant CouponSvc as "coupon-service"
participant Pipeline as "计价管道\n(可配置步骤)"
participant Apollo as "Apollo配置中心"

== 下单计价 ==
User -> OrderCore: 提交订单
OrderCore -> PriceSvc: POST /api/v1/price/calculate (items, user, coupons)

PriceSvc -> Pipeline: 开始计价
Pipeline -> Apollo: 获取配置 pricing.pipeline.steps
Apollo --> Pipeline: ["BASIC","MEMBER","PROMOTION","COUPON","SHIPPING","TAX"]

== Step 1: BasicPricer ==
Pipeline -> Pipeline: BasicPricer → unitPrice = SKU原价
Pipeline --> Pipeline: lineTotal = unitPrice * quantity

== Step 2: MemberPricer ==
Pipeline -> MemberSvc: GET /members/{userId}/price-rate
MemberSvc --> Pipeline: {tier: "DIAMOND", discountRate: 0.9}
Pipeline -> Pipeline: MemberPricer → memberPrice = unitPrice * 0.9
Pipeline --> Pipeline: memberDiscount = unitPrice - memberPrice

== Step 3: PromoPricer ==
Pipeline -> PromoSvc: 查询可用促销 (items, total)
PromoSvc --> Pipeline: [{type:"FULL_REDUCTION", reduce:50}]
Pipeline -> Pipeline: 验证叠加互斥 (memberPrice x FULL_REDUCTION → ✅ 可叠加)
Pipeline -> Pipeline: PromoPricer → promoDiscount = -50
Pipeline --> Pipeline: afterPromo = memberPrice - promoDiscount

== Step 4: CouponPricer ==
Pipeline -> CouponSvc: 查询可用优惠券 (user, items)
CouponSvc --> Pipeline: [{type:"CASH", value:30}]
Pipeline -> Pipeline: 验证券叠加互斥 (FULL_REDUCTION x CASH → ✅ 可叠加)
Pipeline -> CouponSvc: POST /lock (幂等, 预占券)
CouponSvc --> Pipeline: {locked: true}
Pipeline -> Pipeline: CouponPricer → couponDiscount = -30
Pipeline --> Pipeline: afterCoupon = afterPromo - couponDiscount

== Step 5: ShippingPricer ==
Pipeline -> MemberSvc: GET /members/{userId}/shipping-policy
MemberSvc --> Pipeline: {level: "DIAMOND", freeShipping: true}
Pipeline -> Pipeline: ShippingPricer → shippingFee = 0 (VIP免运费)

== Step 6: TaxPricer ==
Pipeline -> Pipeline: TaxPricer → tax = afterCoupon * taxRate

== 汇总结果 ==
Pipeline --> Pipeline: 计算汇总
Pipeline --> PriceSvc: PricingResult
PriceSvc --> OrderCore: {finalTotal, 各步骤明细}

OrderCore --> User: 订单确认 (最终金额: ¥XXX.XX)

@enduml
